All names clearly reveal intent.

## Step 2: Calculate Current APP Mass

```
type Quote = { premium: number };

const PROCESSING_FEE = 5;
const BASE_PREMIUM_BY_TYPE = { sword: 100, amulet: 60, staff: 80 };

const basePremiumFor = (item) => BASE_PREMIUM_BY_TYPE[item.type];

export const quote = (input) => {
  const itemsTotal = input.items.reduce(
    (sum, item) => sum + basePremiumFor(item),
    0,
  );
  return { premium: itemsTotal + PROCESSING_FEE };
};

export const claim = (_input) => { return undefined; };
```

